  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.1">
<l>pōyppā ṭuṭaiyaniṉ tantaiyun tāḻttāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">porutiṟaṟ cañcaṉ kaṭiyaṉ</l>
<l>kāppāru millai kaṭalvaṇṇā vuṉṉait</l>
<l rend="indent">taṉiyēpō yeṅkun tiriti</l>
<l>pēyppāl mulaiyuṇṭa pittaṉē kēcava</l>
<l rend="indent">nampiyuṉ ṉaikkātu kutta</l>
<l>vāyppālar peṇṭuka ḷellārum vantā</l>
<l rend="indent">raṭaikkāy tiruttināṉ vaittēṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The father of you who possesses greatness,</l>
<l rend="indent">having gone [and] being delayed,</l>
<l>there is no one to protect you from the cruel Kaṃsa,</l>
<l rend="indent">with power to battle,</l>
<l>O Ocean-hued One, would [you] go alone,</l>
<l rend="indent">wandering everywhere?</l>
<l>O Crazy One who drank the milk from the breast of the demoness!</l>
<l rend="indent">Kēcava! Dear One!</l>
<l>All the ladies from the cow-herd village have come</l>
<l rend="indent">to pierce your ears [and] I have prepared the areca nut.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
